considerably lower.

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:54.250
Wilson's scathing critiques of
congress in the late 19th century

00:04:54.250 --> 00:04:56.930
and early 20th century of
course, weren't the first

00:04:56.930 --> 00:05:00.120
to lament the inefficiencies
of the legislature

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:01.540
or declare the separation

00:05:01.540 --> 00:05:04.920
