outmoded in the modern world.

00:05:04.920 --> 00:05:06.810
But they were however
among the first

00:05:06.810 --> 00:05:09.720
to systematically diagnose
the problem as one

00:05:09.720 --> 00:05:13.100
that could perhaps be overcome
or at least improved upon

00:05:13.100 --> 00:05:16.420
through purposeful
institutional change

00:05:16.420 --> 00:05:19.520
and he certainly was not
the last to claim this.

00:05:19.520 --> 00:05:22.120
This celebrated tradition
carries on to today,

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:24.880
in fact you don't even need to
specify what branch you're talking

00:05:24.880 --> 00:05:27.700
